title: Baldface Mountain (Herkimer County, New York)
text: Baldface Mountain is a <a href="mountain">mountain</a> located in <a href="Adirondack%20Mountains">Adirondack Mountains</a> of <a href="New%20York%20%28state%29">New York</a> located in the Town of <a href="Indian%20Lake%2C%20New%20York">Indian Lake</a> south of <a href="Indian%20Lake%20%28hamlet%29%2C%20New%20York">Indian Lake</a>.
